    "This research study addresses the limitations of traditional cryptographic methods for detecting position spoofing attacks.",
    "However, challenges such as imbalanced data and potential overfitting were identified in supervised learning.",
    "Authors suggest exploring unsupervised approaches and edge computing for partial aggregation to improve scalability and performance in real-world deployment of (ITS).",
    "Synthesis and Analysis: The studies summarized in Table 5 demonstrate the diverse applications of MLPs within federated learning frameworks and their role in enhancing privacy, efficiency, and anomaly detection capabilities.",
